criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  BMI<35 kg/m2

          -  Problem in using socket

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Diabetes;

          -  Peripheral vascular diseases;

          -  Psychiatric problems;

          -  Pregnancy;

          -  Rheumatoid arthritis;

          -  Neurovascular diseases;

          -  Neurological deficits;

          -  Amputation of the contralateral limb;

          -  Infections in progress;

          -  Immunosuppression;
